  [ 86] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [ 87] lt ...................................... <deltaV < 0>
  [ 88] jmpifz [106] ............................ if deltaV < 0 then / else
  [ 91] pushint8 3 .............................. <3>
  [ 93] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [ 95] extcall 145 ............................. <PI>
  [ 97] mul ..................................... <3 * PI>
  [ 98] pushint8 2 .............................. <2>
  [100] div ..................................... <3 * PI / 2>
  [101] setlocal 2 .............................. angle = 3 * PI / 2
  [103] jmp [109]
  [106] pushzero ................................ <0>
